message: "If you use this in research, please cite it."
title: "tpu-trc-quickstart: an AI-driven TRC TPU provisioning skill"
abstract: >-
  A command-line, AI-agent-driven quickstart for provisioning Google TPU Research
  Cloud (TRC) free TPUs (queue, claim, SSH, health check) without touching the GCP
  console. Distilled and sanitized from a real research project (an
  agent-based simulator, MATLAB to JAX/TPU port).
